v0.1.0

2026-06-18

## Initial release

- Forked from `accessible-minimalism` Hugo theme by Leon Stafford (https://github.com/leonstafford/accessible-minimalism-hugo-theme).
- Maintained as an independent theme with additional Hugo compatibility and accessibility improvements.
- Improved Hugo 0.163+ compatibility.
- Migrated language metadata from deprecated `LanguageCode` to `Language.Locale`.
- Enabled support for raw HTML blocks in Markdown files via Goldmark renderer configuration.
- XHTML 1.0 Strict compliant markup.
- Improved accessibility with enlarged default typography (150% base font size, 500% h1 heading size).


